name: Woods Against Eternity
description:
It's lost & found track, back in 2019. This track was originally produced for "KANON EP" but unluckily my laptop died. The master file got corrupted and the vst files are missing. With only a draft wav file, rework it again and remastered it. 
And, Voila~ 

Let us dive into remnants of the post-apocalyptic world controlled by gigantic plants, and mutated survivors.

[Collect and you can get the audio file upon request. For personal non-commercial use]
